detailed_description:
A custom Nyx combat frame.<br />
It wields shields on its shoulders with the word &quot;&quot;Phantasia&quot;&quot; inscribed onto them. What could that mean?<br />
This ridable, powered exoskeleton covers the soldier's entire body, protecting them from bombs and other dangers while providing the full range of human movement. It houses thrusts on its back, allowing the user to fly for a short period of time by pressing and holding the jump button.&quot;

